    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><p><i>1st-level Clockwork Soul feature</i></p><p>Your connection to the plane of absolute order allows you to equalize chaotic moments. When a creature you can see within 60 feet of you is about to roll a [[/r d20]] with advantage or disadvantage, you can use your reaction to prevent the roll from being affected by advantage and disadvantage.</p><p>You can use this feature a number of times equal to your proficiency bonus, and you regain all expended uses when you finish a long rest.</p></div>",
